        <Parent_String>doorway components [300002784], doorways and doorway components [300052372], openings by form [300114196], openings (architectural elements) [300002765], openings and opening components [300052369], architectural elements [300000885], components by specific context [300241584], components (objects parts) [300241583], Components (hierarchy name) [300241490], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
